# 📁 `data/` Folder

This folder should contain the input files used in the solar wind data analysis.  
**These files are not versioned** in this repository to avoid issues with large file sizes or license restrictions.

## 📂 Expected Data Types

- **ACE Data (CDF format):**
  - Example filename: `ACE_BROWSE_2015-001_to_2015-365.CDF`
  - Source: [NASA CDAWeb](https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/)

- **OMNI Data (CDF format):**
  - Example filename: `omni_min2015.dat`
  - Source: [NASA CDAWeb](https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/)


## 🔖 Notes

- Files must be placed manually in this folder.
- Large or temporary binary files are ignored by Git (see `.gitignore`).
- You may organize files by type or year if needed (e.g., `cdf/`, `omni/`, `hdf/`).
